Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,True Calendar year 71.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In this year, which would later come be known as the first year of the Third Galactic Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,humanity was in the midst of expanding its sphere of activity beyond Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The development of Dyson Spheres accelerated humanity's progress into space,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and 70% of the total population now resides in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is JIOR Sphere No. 1, Module 77. Please transmit your country of registration
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.73,0:00:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is GS2776 flight 21. Requesting docking clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Registry confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You are cleared to dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You are carrying two transfer students for Sakimori Academy, is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wash it down with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:04.38,Alt,,0,0,0,,Prove your manliness, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose, Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.76,0:01:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is still neck and neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Tokishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the home stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:14.27,Alt,,0,0,0,,Finish 'em off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite a ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's apparently an eating contest to decide who gets to use the school field.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe high schoolers would still be fighting over who gets to use the track...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.37,0:01:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's fine. At least it's peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We were counting on you, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:45.52,Alt,,0,0,0,,Way to blow it, Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I didn't want to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't matter. We rock-paper-scissored for it, and you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The odds of the loser winning the next time are—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:02:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero. Totally zero. Haruto has absolutely no head for competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone in a weird shirt like that has no room to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You, Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to JIOR Module 77.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather in the module is fair today, and— Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your manifest said that there were two transfer students.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace has made this JIOR country soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, this was settled by the balance of power between the countries of Dorssia and ARUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The defining characteristic of both countries is that they developed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and expanded by means of multinational treaties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell us what will be on the test, already!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you expect, this school has only been open for three years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it would be a total hassle to go back to Earth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey this school is really pretty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How do I register someone as a Wired friend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey have you heard the story about the legendary shrine?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah! They say it'll make sure your love is reciprocated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So anyway have you heard?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They say the Dorssia Mil-Fed is violating our territorial space again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i0}They'll probably settle with us by paying a fine.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Geez, again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Man that's so lame.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm fine with it. It's more economical than having a military right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You saying that sums up everything that's wrong with this country.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey Haruto. Aren't you ever going to tell Shoko how you feel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's up?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's nothing. Just forget it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.90,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(590,328)\frz339.7}She's gonna get snatchet up\Nby somebody else.\NDon't come crying to me\Nwhen she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been staring at me like a freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You have something on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing! Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's nothing, then you shouldn't mind me seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, there's nothing on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Give it back! If you don't give it back you and I are through as friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then answer me. Why were you looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only thinking, "She'd be beautiful, if she kept quiet...."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wha—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I just mean, maybe you could keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A restriction or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm not?! When I talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'm a... beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not right, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So which am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, to be young...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Inuzuka-senpai, you're always talking about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I plan to become the richest person in the world someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to dream dream big, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, could we trouble you for directions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skirt is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Butt out. I'm talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so uptight. Are you asking her to the dance or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer to mind my manners at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We should keep contact with the locals to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Do you know the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The sprinklers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The sprinklers are spaced one every 13 meters,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but they change to one every 12.5 meters in front of just that structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 40 desks in each classroom visible through the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Student body, 480.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the structure was built using common layered construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,From a load-bearing standpoint, there is no room for extra facility personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:06:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I must therefore conclude that it is beneath the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What year are those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen them around before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer students, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have enough passion in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Our throwdown earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't go into it intending to win, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... I wish we lived in a world where there wasn't stuff like winning and losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We each could have used half the field just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Halfsies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you use a knife to cut the yolk of your ham & eggs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and the girl you love in half, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness can't be split into "halfsies".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what year are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back, Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do if someone hits you even when you don't want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Laugh foolishly and concede defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't concede, your only choice is to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Nanami, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to give Rukino extra lessons, but she isn't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the celebrity...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd... I wonder if I told her the wrong time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:47.30,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1\frz20.78\fs30\pos(658,96)}List of students\Nsigned up for\Nextra lessons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, what was that guy's deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, pal, but I'm the kind of girl who eats the egg white first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyway, the star of ham & eggs is the ham!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, the ham is key.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And Haruto was the one who was knocked down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What Haruto said was totally noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't wrong, so what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting angry so I don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me feel a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what friends are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you never get mad at anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We were supposed to keep contact to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:55.65,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"May my love come true."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making a wish, too, Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They say if you profess your feelings here, your feelings are sure to be returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a legendary shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Schools that were built three years ago don't have old legends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Message from L-elf:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bats fly across the cloudy sky."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Colonel's star pupil for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Message to fatherland:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Commencing Operation Virgin Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Blitzendegen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Give me a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, t-this is—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Waffe unit #1, box out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko, I'm in—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of low, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What a racket...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably a drill or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't those Waffe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorssians?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What military is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorssian model number NW507Be, manned Waffe units!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are all those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, get inside the school building! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A war?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell, man...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hostiles confirmed as Dorssia Mil-Fed fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Send word to the homeland!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use! I can't get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would the Dorssian military attack us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't anyone get through to the homeland?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They say they're being blown out of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,JIOR is a neutral country!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's use the Valvrave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna take responsibility for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm impressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, he hogged all the fun again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This one was still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone inside that car!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine! Go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be playing hide-and-seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out! Okay, Shoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto, she's—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave! She might—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to accept it! She's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make them pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto! It's not safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just sit tight until some adults arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make them pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make them pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make them pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe here, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's humanoid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander! It's the primary strategic objective!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you failed, you punks... I told them so!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drag out just the pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just need a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Work! Work! You're a robot, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to avenge Shoko! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Work! Come on, work! Work, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This will spread the word...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reports on the, sneak attack against JIOR by the Dorssian army are still spotty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The government is struggling to respond.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:36.25,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's getting pounded!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that a JIOR machine?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hey, this is-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're a weapon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I beaten...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dying without getting revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Shoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I blew it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You didn't go into it intending to win, did you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you can't concede, you have to fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It transformed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Its color and power are different, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't lose to a military that's never known war!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too fast?! Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What kind of light is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We did it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:22.35,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thermal limits exceeded.\NSystems shut down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in the class next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the boy from this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen him before somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:41.86,Alt,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Him and me, we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a kid in there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not a soldier?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's JIOR's secret weapon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They say he's a high-schooler!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why does he have a robot?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the guy who lost this morning!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Way to go, Mr. Tokishima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.71,0:22:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you said, a world without winners and losers is a fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.22,0:23:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain L-elf, Dorssian Special Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I won again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...Lieselotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.62,0:24:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, episode 2, "Beyond 666".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.17,0:24:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Valvrave the Liberator; it's the system to reveal the truth of the world.
